{"word":"πρόπαρ","slug":"πρόπαρ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πρόπαρ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:παρά'><el>παρά</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Preposition'><a href='S:Preposition'>prep.</a></a> with <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>before, in front of</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <i>before, sooner</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}